QUIZ: Which Celebrity Serial Dater Are You? Do you play the game of love like one of these stars? by Soraya Joseph 2h ago 
Some say that the quickest way to get over someone, is to get under with someone else. These celebs have proven that when it comes to matters of the heart, they waste no time moving on, and honestly we can’t hate. That’s why we’ve put together this quiz of celebrities whose love lives have made headlines as much (if not more) than their actual careers. 
So which serial-dating star are you? 
Having trouble with finding love? You’re not the only one. Check out a timeline of T.Swifts relationships.
